#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.audiotube.appdata.xml:125
msgid ""
"AudioTube can search YouTube Music, list albums and artists, play "
"automatically generated playlists, albums and allows to put your own "
"playlist together. It is adapted to mobile phones and desktop computers."
msgstr ""
"Ar „AudioTube“ varat meklēt „YouTube Music“, uzskaitīt albumus un "
"izpildītājus, atskaņot automātiski izveidotus repertuārus, albumus un veidot "
"savu repertuāru. Programma ir piemērota lietošanai mobilajos tālruņos un "
"datoros."
